      <h1>Gifts</h1>

      <h2>Cash?</h2>
      <p>Why yes, we will gladly accept your hard-earned fiat currency. We quite enjoy the feeling of depositing a paper cheque in the bank, but feel free to send an Interac&reg; or Zelle&reg; to Will or Amanda if preferred.</p>

      <h2>Registry?</h2>
      <p>Sure, we have one of those. <a href="Registry">Check it out here</a> if that's more your jam.</p>

      <h2>Something Not On the Registry?</h2>
      <p>You do you, man/lady/non-binary-person. Wow us with your skills.</p>

      <h2>No Gift At All?</h2>
      <p>I mean... a Spotify "mixed tape" would be nice, at least, but sure, we'd rather that you came with nothing than that you didn't come at all!</p>


